item.title: Zorbio
item.description: Zorbio is a free multiplayer eat-em-up game that you can play in your browser! Zorbio is brought to you by my good friend Jared Sprague and I, via our small game development company, Scripta, Inc. Follow Zorbio development on the Scripta blog, or on Facebook. Play now!
